PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT ?stateLabel WHERE {
  wd:Q2695156 wdt:P1353 ?city .
  ?city wdt:P131 ?state .
  ?state rdfs:label ?stateLabel .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?stateLabel ) = "en" )
}

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT ?merkelYear ?blairYear WHERE {
  wd:Q567 wdt:P569 ?merkelBirth .
  wd:Q9545 wdt:P569 ?blairBirth .
  BIND( YEAR( ?merkelBirth ) AS ?merkelYear ) .
  BIND( YEAR( ?blairBirth ) AS ?blairYear ) .
  FILTER ( ?merkelYear = ?blairYear )
}

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX dct: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?label ?description WHERE {
  wd:Q18032040 rdfs:label ?label .
  wd:Q18032040 dct:description ?description .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?label ) = 'en' ) .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?description ) = 'en' )
}

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT ?animal WHERE {
  wd:Q625657 wdt:P1359 ?operation .
  ?operation wdt:P800 ?animal .
  ?animal wdt:P31 wd:Q146 .
}

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT ?movie ?movieLabel WHERE {
  ?movie wdt:P179 wd:Q462 .
  ?movie rdfs:label ?movieLabel .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?movieLabel ) = 'en' )
}

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
ASK WHERE {
  wd:Q1650 wdt:P2043 ?weserLength .
  wd:Q584 wdt:P2043 ?rhineLength .
  FILTER ( ?weserLength > ?rhineLength )
}

PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT ?event ?eventLabel WHERE {
  ?event wdt:P31 wd:Q1190554 .
  ?event wdt:P585 ?date .
  FILTER ( ?date >= "1910-01-01T00:00:00Z" ^^ xsd:dateTime && ?date <= "1920-12-31T23:59:59Z" ^^ xsd:dateTime ) ?event wdt:P1120 ?deaths .
  ?event rdfs:label ?eventLabel .
  FILTER ( lang( ?eventLabel ) = "en" && ?deaths > 50000000 )
}
ORDER BY DESC ( ?deaths )
LIMIT 1

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT ?country ?countryLabel WHERE {
  wd:Q5451 wdt:P17 ?country .
  ?country rdfs:label ?countryLabel .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?countryLabel ) = 'en' )
}

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT ?state WHERE {
  wd:Q2926117 wdt:P19 ?birthplace1 .
  wd:Q87192979 wdt:P19 ?birthplace2 .
  ?birthplace1 wdt:P131 + wd:Q183 .
  ?birthplace2 wdt:P131 + wd:Q183 .
  BIND( wd:Q183 AS ?state )
}

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
SELECT ( COUNT( DISTINCT ?president ) AS ?count ) WHERE {
  ?president p:P39 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P39 wd:Q218295 .
  ?statement pq:P580 ?start .
  FILTER ( ?start > "1990-01-01" ^^ xsd:date )
}

PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT ?service ?serviceLabel WHERE {
  wd:Q70209136 wdt:P144 ?service .
  ?service rdfs:label ?serviceLabel .
  FILTER ( LANG( ?serviceLabel ) = 'en' )
}
